title: Gifted two of my friends skins, neither of them received them.
body: Bought two friends skins neither of them received them. (DogeWizard) (WIggeh)

replies.body: I've got both of those accounts pulled up and they did both recently get the gifts you sent. Wiggeh got a skin for Kayn and Doge got a skin for Soraka.
RP was taken and it shows in my gifting history.
